---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Monthly Box">
  <main>
    <div class="bg-white h-screen">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between py-16">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h1
              class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl"
            >
              Monthly Box
            </h1>
            <p
              class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
            >
            Hey there, cycle sisters! Are you tired of dealing with your period like it's a curse? Well, we've got a surprise for you! Introducing our brand new monthly subscription boxes curated just for menstruating individuals.
            </p>
            <p
            class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
            >
            Each box is packed with period essentials, self-care treats, and surprise goodies that will make you feel like the queen of the world (or at least of your cycle). Think delicious chocolates, cozy socks, natural skincare products, and more.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0">Don't let your period get you down â€“ sign up for our monthly subscription box and get ready to party (in your PJs, of course). You'll get a surprise in the mail every month, and you'll never have to worry about running out of period essentials again.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0">Join the period party and sign up now to be the first to know when we launch. And as a thank-you for being an early bird, we're offering an exclusive discount on your first box. So what are you waiting for? Let's get this menstrual show on the road!</p>

          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 md:mt-0 md:w-1/2">
            <div class="max-w-md mx-auto sm:max-w-lg md:max-w-xl">
              <div class="mt-8 sm:flex w-64 h-64 mx-auto">
              <!-- image for product  -->
              <img
                src="https://bryces-images.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/demophoto.png"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-md"
                />
              </div>
              <form class="mt-8 sm:flex justify-center">
                <input
                  aria-label="Email address"
                  type="email"
                  required
                  class="appearance-none rounded w-full px-5 py-3 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 sm:max-w-xs"
                  placeholder="Enter your email"
                />
                <div
                  class="mt-3 rounded-md shadow sm:mt-0 sm:ml-3 sm:flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-400 hover:bg-indigo-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                  >
                    Notify Me
                  </button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
